snippet.textDisplay:
I'm a Muslim and i feel sorry for us and them who has used Iqbal's R.A kalaam as this.
We never understand the teachings of this we just enjoy it.
I feel sorry for these people who sing this with this type of music in back. 
Wallaahi it becomes harram.
He has written it for us, to understand it to learn from it but Alas we just enjoy it.
And for those people who feel goosebumps by listening to it for read it once and try to understand what Iqbal R.A is trying to teach us, Wallaahi you will change.
